Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像深夏的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的
